  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我們來畫這個語音翻譯系統的狀態圖。核心流程是從閒置開始，按下錄音按鈕進入Recording狀態，這邊需要VAD持續監控和即時更新。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "Recording",
        "VAD"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "了解，所以Idle是起點，然後有兩個方向可以離開Recording？除了正常檢測到語音結束進入Processing，還要有使用者取消回到Idle對嗎？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "Recording",
        "Processing"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "對，取消流程很重要。然後Processing之後要分兩路：如果TTS啟用就進Playing播放語音，如果停用就直接回Idle顯示文字結果。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Processing",
        "Playing",
        "TTS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主流程畫出來。另外Processing是不是也需要錯誤處理？比如ASR或翻譯引擎出問題的時候。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Processing",
        "ASR",
        "翻譯引擎"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "沒錯，Processing失敗要進Error狀態。Error有兩種出口：一般錯誤讓使用者確認後回Idle，嚴重錯誤則直接終止系統到結束點。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Processing",
        "Error",
        "Idle",
        "終止點"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Playing結束後也是回到Idle嗎？還有使用者中斷播放的情況要處理嗎？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Playing",
        "Idle",
        "中斷"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "兩種情況都回Idle，播放完成或使用者中斷都重置狀態。最後幫我在Recording和Processing旁邊加上註解，說明內部在做什麼，比如ASR轉錄、翻譯引擎處理這些細節。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Recording",
        "Processing",
        "ASR",
        "翻譯引擎",
        "註解"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成了。Recording旁邊標了VAD監控和音訊串流，Processing旁邊標了ASR轉錄、翻譯和儲存對話記錄。整個狀態圖從初始化到可能的嚴重錯誤終止都覆蓋到了。",
